{
  "_comment": "Edit this file to personalize what vault files auto-load when you ask strategic questions. The vault-context hook reads this on every prompt. Add your own topics as entries in the topics list. Each topic has a name (for your own reference), triggers (keywords that activate it), and files (vault-relative paths to inject). Remove or edit any example below. Delete this file entirely if you only want the core files (Current Priorities, Open Loops).",

